children.name: Rules
children.text:
☆ Skyrim Rant
Bore an enemy NPC with a Skyrim rant, making their next move deal 50% less damage.

☆ Burn
Burn an enemy NPC with 1d8 damage,
"Just like how he burnt the soup."

☆ Random Delivery
Give a 1d6 heal to a random NPC
*Includes enemy NPCs

"It's the weird man card, you can play it, but there will be consequences."
